queries.sql: SELECT `properties`.*, `agents`.`name` AS `agent_name`, `agents`.`username` AS `agent_username`, `agents`.`email` AS `agent_email`, `agents`.`phone` AS `agent_phone`, `agents`.`address` AS `agent_address`, `agents`.`govt_id` AS `agent_govt_id`, `agents`.`company_name` AS `agent_company`, `agents`.`photo` AS `agent_photo`, `agents`.`status` AS `agent_status`, `agents`.`paid` AS `agent_paid`, `categories`.`name` AS `category_name`, `locations`.`city` AS `location_city`, `locations`.`state` AS `location_state`, `locations`.`country` AS `location_country`, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT property_images.image_url) AS images, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT features.name) AS features FROM `properties` LEFT JOIN `agents` ON `agents`.`id` = `properties`.`user_id` LEFT JOIN `categories` ON `categories`.`id` = `properties`.`category_id` LEFT JOIN `locations` ON `locations`.`id` = `properties`.`location_id` LEFT JOIN `property_images` ON `property_images`.`property_id` = `properties`.`id` LEFT JOIN `property_features` ON `property_features`.`property_id` = `properties`.`id` LEFT JOIN `features` ON `features`.`id` = `property_features`.`feature_id` WHERE `properties`.`prop_url` = 'semi-detached' GROUP BY `properties`.`id` ORDER BY `properties`.`id` ASC LIMIT 1
